    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to preserve its legendary 50/50 weight distribution and handling characteristics. Recent preventative maintenance includes a Vanos overhaul and a precision valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain operates within factory tolerances. A mechanically honest machine optimized for lateral Gs and linear power delivery.",
